         <div type="level1">
            <head>Arabic transcriptions</head>
            <p>In general, the same transcription system as that of the EAe is
  applied. However, Hamzat qaṭʿ is always to be transcribed. Titles and
  names are transcribed without case endings:</p>
            <p>
               <hi rendition="simple:italic">Šarḥ sabab intiqāl mamlakat Sulaymān
  malik ʾIsrāʾīl ʾilā bilād an-naǧāšīya allatī hiya al-ḥabaša</hi>
            </p>
